comments: Looney (GSW) contests Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) jump shot attempt and moves into his space, causing more than marginal lower-body contact after Gilgeous-Alexander's release.
Williams (OKC) moves alongside Curry's (GSW) path and marginal body contact occurs as he releases away during the driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Wiggins (GSW) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Wiggins is moving towards Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) when illegal contact occurs, which is before he makes contact with the ball.
Wiggins (GSW) gathers the pass on his left foot and takes one step before releasing the ball at the start of his dribble.
Curry (GSW) is dislodging the ball simultaneously as marginal arm contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) in the backcourt.
Joe (OKC) does not release his shot attempt before the shot clock expires.
Looney (GSW) establishes himself in Wallace's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact that occurs during the pick.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Curry's (GSW) arm after the release.
Looney (GSW) brings his arm forward and slides his hand off Holmgren's (OKC) body during the layup attempt, and the contact is marginal.
Wallace (OKC) is aligning alongside Curry's (GSW) path when marginal body contact occurs after Curry's gather.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) legally contests Wiggins' (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Wiggins (GSW) legally contests Holmgren's (OKC) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Looney (GSW) contests Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Looney (GSW) firms up over his right foot in Dort's (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs as the screen is set.
Wiggins (GSW) legally contests Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Paul (GSW) is firming up over his left foot in Dort's (OKC) path when marginal contact occurs to Dort's side on the pick.
Curry (GSW) brings his arm toward Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) space and marginal contact occurs as Curry releases away to shoot.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) cleanly blocks Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Paul (GSW) jumps alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and slides his hand off Gilgeous-Alexander's body during the driving shot attempt.
Williams (OKC) closes out to the side and legally contests Wiggins's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Williams (OKC) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Looney (GSW) commits a take foul on Williams (OKC). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Paul (GSW) commits a take foul on Williams (OKC).
Williams (OKC) is moving alongside Wiggins' (GSW) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Williams (OKC) moves alongside Wiggins' (GSW) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Williams (OKC) is still in possession of the ball when the shot clock expires.
